---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Solar &amp; Battery Cardinia Shire | Full Service Area | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="CEC-accredited solar panel &amp; battery installers across the Cardinia Shire - Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes, Lakeside, Heritage Springs, Beaconsfield. Cheaper Home Batteries rebate, STCs, United Energy approved."
  canonical="https://pakenhamsolarbattery.com.au/cardinia-shire/">
  <Fragment slot="head">
</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cardinia Shire &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>Solar &amp; battery across the <span class="accent">Cardinia Shire</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From Officer in the west to the eastern townships, Cardinia Lakes in the south to
        the rural fringe in the north. CEC-accredited solar, Tesla Powerwall &amp; battery
        storage, EV chargers and servicing &mdash; rebate-ready, United Energy approved.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>Local solar guides &mdash; typical roof size, the right system, what we usually spec.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/lakeside/">Lakeside</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other Cardinia Shire localities.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham (CBD)</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham East</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Nar Nar Goon</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Beaconsfield Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Gembrook</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Maryknoll</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Tynong</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bunyip</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Garfield</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cora Lynn</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Tonimbuk</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Two zones, two solar conversations.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Growth-corridor zone</strong> (Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes,
          Lakeside, Pakenham East): young families and new builds with large, north-facing
          solar-ready roofs. Around 255 new dwellings a year &mdash; Pakenham East alone is
          planned for 7,000-plus homes &mdash; so a steady stream of first-time
          <a href="/services/solar-panel-installation/">solar installs</a> and EV-ready
          systems. Cost-of-living pressure makes a <a href="/services/solar-battery-systems/">solar
          + battery system</a> an easy yes here.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Established &amp; rural-fringe zone</strong> (Heritage Springs,
          Beaconsfield, Pakenham Upper, Beaconsfield Upper, Gembrook): larger and acreage
          homes with bigger roofs and bigger evening loads, wanting 10&ndash;13kW arrays,
          larger <a href="/services/battery-storage/">batteries</a> with whole-home backup,
          and three-phase work. This is also where the corridor&rsquo;s decade-old solar
          base is now due for <a href="/services/solar-repairs-servicing/">servicing and
          battery retrofits</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">2026 rebates across the Shire.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cheaper Home Batteries Program:</strong> federal 30% discount, around $252 per usable kWh in 2026, tapering later &mdash; the surge driver.</li>
          <li><strong>Solar STCs:</strong> applied to panels as an upfront discount by your CEC-accredited installer.</li>
          <li><strong>Solar Victoria:</strong> rebate and interest-free loan eligibility checked for your address.</li>
          <li><strong>United Energy:</strong> DNSP pre-approval and AS/NZS 4777 export design on every grid-connected install.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five services</span>
      <h2>What we install.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/solar-panel-installation/"><h3>Solar panel installation</h3><p>Tier-1 Trina, Jinko, REC panels with Fronius/Sungrow inverters. STCs applied.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/battery-storage/"><h3>Battery storage</h3><p>Tesla Powerwall 3, Sungrow &amp; BYD. 2026 Cheaper Home Batteries rebate applied.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/solar-battery-systems/"><h3>Solar + battery systems</h3><p>One hybrid design, every rebate stacked. Best-value bill cut.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/ev-charger-installation/"><h3>EV charger installation</h3><p>Tesla, Zappi, Wallbox integrated with solar so you charge on free sun.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/solar-repairs-servicing/"><h3>Solar repairs &amp; servicing</h3><p>Inverter faults, underperforming systems, any brand. Diagnose &amp; fix.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free quote anywhere in the Cardinia Shire.</h2>
        <p>Growth corridor or rural fringe. Bills checked, rebates confirmed, fixed quote.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
